WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Animal tracks tell mathematical stories!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We can measure footprint sizes and count track patterns.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Different animals leave different shapes and spacing.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Tracking teaches us about measurement and observation.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Mathematics helps us understand wildlife behaviour!